  "description": {
    "zh": "我知道现在到处都很艰难。你有没有对人类适应任何环境的能力感到惊叹？\n\n我认为正是这让人成为了进化的巅峰。但感觉自己在慢慢习惯家乡成群结队的感染者……这让我恶心。\n\n对枪械的需求急剧上升，我在想如果疫情拖延下去，仓库里就只剩手枪了。你能测试一下它们在当前环境下的效果吗？",
    "en": "It's tough everywhere right now, I know. Have you ever been fascinated by this human ability to adapt to any condition?\n\nI think it's what made man the pinnacle of evolution. But to feel like you're slowly getting used to the crowds of infected people in your hometown... It makes me sick.\n\nThe demand for firearms has increased tremendously, and I'm thinking that if this epidemic drags on, there will be only handguns left in the stockpiles. Can you test to see how effective they are in the current environment?"
  },
